Name: Frog struggles
About the game: Frog struggles is a short action game about bugs that live in a pond, watch out for hostile bugs, water, and the big frog... Features 10-20 minutes of playtime. Fight other bugs with a stick. Collect various pieces of fruit. Become friends or foes with other tribes. Big frog with a big tongue. Controls Hold Spacebar to fly upwards. WASD keys to steer.
